Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.70,0:43:55.25,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, that was pretty awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.25,0:43:57.70,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And look what you managed to accomplish!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.25,0:44:02.70,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please, please, please
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.70,0:44:05.90,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,can we do a run-through for the fashion show on it right this minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.90,0:44:08.50,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thought you weren't finished with the stitching on your poncho
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.85,0:44:12.10,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I am now
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.10,0:44:13.10,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Get started without me
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.10,0:44:14.35,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've gotta go find Twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.35,0:44:18.35,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Seeing what we've been able to do here might make her embrace the new magic, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.35,0:44:20.00,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Uh, not that she has any
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.10,0:44:26.15,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I just wish you didn't tell them that ridiculous story!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.15,0:44:28.45,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is all too much for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.45,0:44:30.25,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You have to let it go!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.25,0:44:31.40,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.40,0:44:33.25,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He wants her to get rid of the camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.95,0:44:39.75,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.75,0:44:40.95,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sunset Shimmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.95,0:44:42.45,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What were you doing behind that door?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.45,0:44:42.95,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.95,0:44:44.25,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Um, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.25,0:44:47.90,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I, um, lost an earring. Uh, there it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.10,0:44:50.05,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.05,0:44:51.80,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I ran into you
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.80,0:44:53.25,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I really wanted to thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.45,0:44:54.60,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.20,0:44:56.60,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,For the tough love
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.75,0:44:58.80,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Telling me I should get over Twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.80,0:45:00.05,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I needed to hear that
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.05,0:45:01.60,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sure, no problem
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.10,0:45:03.80,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.80,0:45:04.20,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.20,0:45:06.00,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.00,0:45:07.25,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come on, Sunset
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.25,0:45:08.60,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We used to date
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.60,0:45:10.35,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know when something's bothering you
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.25,0:45:13.45,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, here's the deal
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.05,0:45:15.25,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My friend really likes someone
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.25,0:45:17.65,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but I don't think that someone is who she thinks they are
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.65,0:45:19.90,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna upset my friend by telling her what I think
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.90,0:45:21.40,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,because I also want to protect her
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.40,0:45:23.60,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,because if what I think is happening is really happening
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.60,0:45:25.50,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,then she deserves to know
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.50,0:45:26.45,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.70,0:45:28.40,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nnnno
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.60,0:45:31.40,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But what I do know is that your friend is lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.40,0:45:33.45,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,to have someone like you to look out for her
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.45,0:45:34.40,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.40,0:45:35.55,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.55,0:45:38.00,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You know, you've changed a lot since we went out
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.35,0:45:40.75,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're so much... nicer
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.75,0:45:43.15,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thanks. I'm glad you noticed
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.35,0:45:46.00,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Uh, look, maybe you and me
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.00,0:45:48.90,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,we could start over as... friends
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.90,0:45:50.75,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Uh, uh, sounds great
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.75,0:45:51.85,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.15,0:45:53.10,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Cool, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.10,0:45:55.00,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I want to start over later, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.55,0:46:20.15,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ah, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.65,0:46:22.60,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He's definitely up to something!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.75,0:46:29.75,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's Sunset
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.75,0:46:31.65,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She says to meet her by the rock quarry
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.65,0:46:34.10,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I thought we weren't supposed to hike out that far
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.10,0:46:36.35,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She says it's important!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.90,0:46:42.80,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.65,0:46:45.70,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Shhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.75,0:46:52.35,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's going on down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.35,0:46:54.85,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I think it's Gaia Everfree
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.85,0:46:58.35,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Or rather someone who wants us to think she's back
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.35,0:46:59.30,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.60,0:47:08.30,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.95,0:47:11.20,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This place is beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.20,0:47:14.45,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's Equestrian magic here
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.65,0:47:17.15,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can... I can feel it
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.15,0:47:18.35,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.35,0:47:22.00,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I thought Timber was just faking there was a magical nature creature
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.00,0:47:23.40,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you saying it's real?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.40,0:47:24.40,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Timber?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.40,0:47:26.20,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What does he have to do with any of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.20,0:47:27.20,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.50,0:47:31.30,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's all me
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.00,0:47:34.35,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Gloriosa?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.35,0:47:36.35,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But... Timber
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.35,0:47:37.95,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I was sure he was the one
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.95,0:47:41.00,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,trying to make it seem like Gaia Everfree was back
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.00,0:47:43.60,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It was you who was trying to scare everyone away?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.60,0:47:47.55,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I would never try to scare anyone away from Camp Everfree
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.10,0:47:50.60,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My, oh my
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.60,0:47:54.00,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You fell behind on your payments, Gloriosa
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.00,0:47:56.30,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I own the land now
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.50,0:47:59.55,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please, my great grandparents founded this place
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.55,0:48:02.05,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's been in our family for generations!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.05,0:48:04.15,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You have to let the camp stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.15,0:48:06.65,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Instead of turning it into a spa resort
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.65,0:48:11.00,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,that will line my pockets with more money than this camp ever could?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.90,0:48:13.80,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't think so
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.80,0:48:14.85,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.85,0:48:18.65,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I-I-I-I just need a little more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.80,0:48:23.05,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fine. I'll give you 'til the end of the month
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.05,0:48:23.75,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hmph
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.00,0:48:29.55,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What'll I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.10,0:48:34.90,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.50,0:48:46.40,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oof
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.95,0:48:49.10,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.80,0:49:06.20,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You don't know what those things are!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.20,0:49:08.10,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I know what they can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.95,0:49:10.45,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've been practicing!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.45,0:49:12.80,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can control their power now!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.05,0:49:14.85,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You don't know that for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.55,0:49:21.45,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is our camp, and it's being taken away!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.45,0:49:23.95,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If this has to be our last week here
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.95,0:49:26.85,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm going to use whatever it takes to make it count!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.50,0:49:50.85,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You were using magic all over the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.85,0:49:53.20,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I had to tell them something to cover for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.20,0:49:55.05,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What did you want me to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.05,0:49:59.30,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I just wish you didn't tell them that ridiculous story!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.85,0:50:02.15,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is all too much for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.15,0:50:03.85,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You have to let it go!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.50,0:50:09.20,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Timber wasn't talking about letting go of the camp
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.50,0:50:12.85,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He was talking about you letting go of the magical geodes!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.90,0:50:17.75,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All those things you were doing to make this week the best week ever
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.75,0:50:20.10,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Every time you used magic to do them
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.30,0:50:22.80,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,you caused another problem somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.45,0:50:27.65,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Timber was... covering for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.65,0:50:30.20,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How do you know what I was doing with the geodes?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.20,0:50:32.35,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How do you know about the magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.55,0:50:33.75,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can see things
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.15,0:50:35.50,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Feel things
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.50,0:50:37.45,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Because I have magic, too
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.45,0:50:38.95,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And so does she
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.95,0:50:40.40,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And so do our friends
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.70,0:50:43.30,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Gloriosa, Timber wasn't wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.30,0:50:45.55,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should stop using magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.55,0:50:48.25,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Too much of it can be dangerous if you can't control it!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.25,0:50:50.25,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, I got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.25,0:50:53.15,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to use it to save my camp
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.55,0:50:55.95,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I just need more power!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.95,0:50:57.35,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.20,0:51:16.60,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sorry, girls
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.60,0:51:18.55,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know what I need to do
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.55,0:51:20.75,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I feel like we're not on the same page
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.75,0:51:22.00,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.90,0:51:25.00,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Gloriosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.00,0:51:32.60,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.40,0:51:45.80,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Where are Twilight and Sunset?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.50,0:51:48.30,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They're missing our dress rehearsal
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.75,0:51:49.70,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Uh-uh
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.40,0:51:52.45,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I suppose we can get started without them
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.45,0:51:54.20,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whenever you're ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.80,0:52:03.85,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hmm, Told you you'd like it
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.95,0:52:06.00,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's alright... I guess
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.80,0:52:08.70,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I do get to keep it after camp though, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.15,0:52:27.65,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She looks... different
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.65,0:52:30.95,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah. She looks... taller
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.65,0:52:37.60,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is only a preview
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.90,0:52:41.25,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've got another entire line I'll debut at the real thing
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.70,0:52:43.95,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why did you stop the–
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.95,0:52:46.50,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh my goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.35,0:52:49.70,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Attention, campers!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.70,0:52:52.00,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's Gaia Everfree!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.00,0:52:53.10,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She's real!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.10,0:52:55.25,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Aah! We're doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.75,0:52:57.00,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Gloriosa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.55,0:52:59.20,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.60,0:53:01.15,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's Gloriosa?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.45,0:53:04.25,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Am I going crazy or are her feet not touching the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.55,0:53:06.55,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Freaky-deaky!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.75,0:53:09.45,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I have an announcement to make!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.45,0:53:14.00,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Filthy Rich wants this to be the last session of Camp Everfree
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.00,0:53:15.30,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But don't worry
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.30,0:53:17.75,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.40,0:53:29.45,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.45,0:53:31.85,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We literally just finished building that!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.70,0:43:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不错，这确实很酷炫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.25,0:43:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你们的成果！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.25,0:44:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托，拜托，拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.70,0:44:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能现在就在这里做一次时装秀彩排吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.90,0:44:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,可是你的披风都还没缝好
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.85,0:44:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,现在缝好了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.10,0:44:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你们先开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.10,0:44:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我得去找下暮光
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.35,0:44:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定她在看到我们的成果后也能坦然面对这新的魔法了！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.35,0:44:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,呃，不过她也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.10,0:44:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我真希望你没给他们讲过那个蠢故事！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.15,0:44:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这对你来说压力太大了！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.45,0:44:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你得学会放手！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.25,0:44:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.40,0:44:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他想让她卖掉营地！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.95,0:44:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.75,0:44:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,余晖烁烁？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.95,0:44:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你在门后面干什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.45,0:44:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.95,0:44:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，没什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.25,0:44:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我-那个-耳环掉了，哈，找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.10,0:44:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，那个
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.05,0:44:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴正好碰到你
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.80,0:44:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我很想谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.45,0:44:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,谢什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.20,0:44:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,谢你对我在感情上的开导
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.75,0:44:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我我应该放下对暮光的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.80,0:45:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这对我帮助很大
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.05,0:45:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.10,0:45:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么不对的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.80,0:45:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.20,0:45:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.00,0:45:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,别装了，余晖
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.25,0:45:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在一起过
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.60,0:45:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我能看出来你在烦恼些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.25,0:45:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.05,0:45:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我的一个朋友喜欢上了一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.25,0:45:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我觉得那个人的本性和我朋友心里的形象完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.65,0:45:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我怕告诉了她我的想法会让她心烦
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.90,0:45:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但因为我又想保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.40,0:45:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,因为如果事情真如我所想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.60,0:45:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,她还是应该知道
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.50,0:45:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,懂了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.70,0:45:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.60,0:45:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我知道能有你这样替人分忧的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.40,0:45:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,她是相当的幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.45,0:45:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.40,0:45:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.55,0:45:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,当初我们一起的时候你还不是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.35,0:45:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的你…更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.75,0:45:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了，真高兴你能看出来
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.35,0:45:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那个，也许我们能…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.00,0:45:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,重新开始…从朋友做起？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.90,0:45:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯嗯，听起来不错
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.75,0:45:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.15,0:45:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,酷，耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.10,0:45:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我也觉得现在重新开始太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.55,0:46:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，该死！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.65,0:46:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他绝对在密谋着什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.75,0:46:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是余晖
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.75,0:46:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,她说去采石场见她
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.65,0:46:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是不能进入那地方吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.10,0:46:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,她说有很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.90,0:46:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.65,0:46:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嘘！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.75,0:46:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,出什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.35,0:46:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得是森灵盖亚
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.85,0:46:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,或者说是某个希望我们认为她回归了的人
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.35,0:46:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,走！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.60,0:47:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,哇...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.95,0:47:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这里真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.20,0:47:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有小马国的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.65,0:47:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我能...我能感觉得到
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.15,0:47:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.35,0:47:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为魔法生物什么的都是云杉捏造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.00,0:47:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你的意思是真的有？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.40,0:47:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,云杉？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.40,0:47:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他又是怎么和这事扯上关系的？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.20,0:47:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.50,0:47:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,都是我干的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.00,0:47:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉兰？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.35,0:47:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,可是……云杉
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.35,0:47:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为是他
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.95,0:47:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,想让大家觉得森灵盖亚回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.00,0:47:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是你想吓跑大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.60,0:47:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想吓跑森灵营地的任何一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.10,0:47:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.60,0:47:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你贷款还慢了啊，嘉兰金菊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.00,0:47:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,现在这块地是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.50,0:47:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了，这里是我曾祖父母创建
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.55,0:48:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,并一代一代传下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.05,0:48:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能把营地拆了！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.15,0:48:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,也不能把这里变成一个水疗度假村
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.65,0:48:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,然后赚到像这种小营地永远都赚不到的大把钞票？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.90,0:48:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.80,0:48:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,求您了！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.85,0:48:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我－我－我－我只是需要一点时间！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.80,0:48:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,也行，这个月底就是最后的期限
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.05,0:48:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.00,0:48:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.10,0:48:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.50,0:48:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.95,0:48:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.80,0:49:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你不了解这些东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.20,0:49:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我知道它们能做些什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.95,0:49:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都在练习！
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.45,0:49:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我已经能控制它们的力量了！
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.05,0:49:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你又没有把握！
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.55,0:49:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的营地都要没了！
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.45,0:49:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这是我们在这里度过的最后一周
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.95,0:49:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就要不惜一切代价办好这最后一次！
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.50,0:49:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你到处使用魔法！
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.85,0:49:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我总得跟他们说点什么幌子吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.20,0:49:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你还希望我怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.05,0:49:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我真希望你没给他们讲过这个蠢故事！
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.85,0:50:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这对你来说压力太大了！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.15,0:50:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你得学会放手！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.50,0:50:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,云杉说的放手不是放弃营地
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.50,0:50:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是说要你放弃这些魔法晶簇
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.90,0:50:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直试着让这周变成最棒露营周
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.75,0:50:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但你一使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.30,0:50:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就又会出现新的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.45,0:50:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,云杉是在……为你打掩护！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.65,0:50:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道我在用这些晶簇？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.20,0:50:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道魔法的事情的？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.55,0:50:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.15,0:50:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我能感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.50,0:50:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我也有魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.45,0:50:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,而且她也有
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.95,0:50:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的朋友们都有
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.70,0:50:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉兰，云杉说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.30,0:50:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你不应该再使用魔法了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.55,0:50:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,强大的魔法若是控制不当是会很危险的！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.25,0:50:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我会搞定的！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.25,0:50:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我要用魔法拯救我的营地
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.55,0:50:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是需要更多力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.95,0:50:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.20,0:51:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉了，两位
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.60,0:51:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我很清楚自己要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.55,0:51:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不过看起来你们两个并不理解我
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.75,0:51:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所以……
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.90,0:51:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉兰！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.00,0:51:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.40,0:51:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,暮光和余晖呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.50,0:51:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,她们要错过我们的彩排了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.75,0:51:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯哼
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.40,0:51:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,还是不等她们了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.45,0:51:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好就开始吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.80,0:52:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,都说过你会喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.95,0:52:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我看…还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.80,0:52:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,露营完了我就可以拿走了，对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.15,0:52:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,她看起来…变了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.65,0:52:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，她看起来…变高了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.65,0:52:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是预展而已
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.90,0:52:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,正式出演的时候我还有另外整整一系列要上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.70,0:52:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你把音乐停了干－
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.95,0:52:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.35,0:52:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,营员们，注意！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.70,0:52:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是森灵盖亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.00,0:52:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她是真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.10,0:52:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们完蛋啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.75,0:52:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉兰？！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.55,0:52:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.60,0:53:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那是嘉兰？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.45,0:53:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是我疯了还是她真的飘起来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.55,0:53:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我怕怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.75,0:53:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我要宣布一件事！
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.45,0:53:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,臭钱想要让这次露营变成森灵营地所举办的最后一次露营
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.00,0:53:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.30,0:53:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我会搞定的！
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.40,0:53:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有搞错！
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.45,0:53:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们才又修好的！
